{"tid":1256683,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【蜘蛛俠：決戰千里】首輪影評出爐　外媒讚大戰精彩：至少睇3次","createTime":"2019-06-25T06:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T16:42:08.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ef59c3c912ece0b1b6b59b2b81a4c350a3d6b16a","tid":1256683,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T06:58:26.000Z","msg":"Marvel Studios本年度最後一擊《蜘蛛俠：決戰千里》（Spider-Man: Far From Home）將於下周上映，美國已率先舉行媒體試映會，首輪影評亦正式出爐，幾乎一致獲得好評，有影評人仲話至少要睇3次先夠！<br />\n<br />\n有影評人指出，電影前半段劇情非常有趣，之後不斷給予觀眾驚喜，片尾大戰可稱得上是史上最精彩的《蜘蛛俠》電影動作場面，達到令人震驚的程度。男主角湯賀蘭（Tom Holland）的演出固然精彩，但飾演「Mysterio」的積佳蘭賀（Jake Gyllenhaal）就更搶鏡，他更被奉為MCU最有趣的角色之一，連Zendaya的演出亦備受讚賞，比喻她為《黑豹》（Black Panther）的Shuri。<br />\n<br />\n相信很多影迷都關心《蜘蛛俠：決戰千里》如何銜接《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers: Endgame）的劇情，影評人指劇情安排恰當，粉絲無需擔心。不過亦有人指出，這一集比《蜘蛛俠：強勢回歸》（Spider-Man: Homecoming）較遜色。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/343119/%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E4%BF%A0-%E6%B1%BA%E6%88%B0%E5%8D%83%E9%87%8C-%E9%A6%96%E8%BC%AA%E5%BD%B1%E8%A9%95%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90-%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E8%AE%9A%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0%E7%B2%BE%E5%BD%A9-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E7%9D%873%E6%AC%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F343119%2F%25E8%259C%2598%25E8%259B%259B%25E4%25BF%25A0-%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%258D%2583%25E9%2587%258C-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E8%25A9%2595%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2588%2590-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E8%25AE%259A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E5%25BD%25A9-%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591%25E7%259D%25873%25E6%25AC%25A1&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443uu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=9b113a5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/343119/%E8%9C%98%E8%9B%9B%E4%BF%A0-%E6%B1%BA%E6%88%B0%E5%8D%83%E9%87%8C-%E9%A6%96%E8%BC%AA%E5%BD%B1%E8%A9%95%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90-%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E8%AE%9A%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B0%E7%B2%BE%E5%BD%A9-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E7%9D%873%E6%AC%A1</a>"},{"pid":"e8d8843f3e5ba3a